@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_bkyjxy(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.abs(v1)
    tmp = (wp.sin(0.76) * wp.cos((v1 + 0.10 * v0 + 0.36)))
    v0 = (wp.abs(v2) - wp.cos(wp.abs(v1 + 0.20)))
    v2 = (0.45 - wp.cos(tmp))
    tmp = (tmp / v1)
    v0 = v0
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.abs(wp.exp(v0 + 0.95)))
    data[tid] = v0
